    dc:description "FIGURES 64–65. Macrorrhyncha borealis n. sp., holotype male. 64. Habitus. Scale = ca. 1.0 mm. 65. Head, anterolateral. Scale = ca. 0.5 mm. Abbreviations: cx1, coxa 1; lbl, labellum." ;
